    {
      "id": "focus-layout-runtime",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Runtime Truth",
      "position": {
        "x": -60,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Runtime Truth\n\nFocus is runtime-only and subjective.\n\n- `focusedNodeId`\n- `focusedFragmentId`\n- navigation events\n- zoom pressure\n- interaction state\n\nDo not persist focus into the graph artifact.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
