    {
      "id": "focus-layout-representation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Representation Truth",
      "position": {
        "x": 420,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Representation Truth\n\nSemantic levels remain stable and deterministic.\n\n- `detail`\n- `summary`\n- `icon`\n- fallback rules\n- role-based rendering\n\nLayout should respond to this model, not replace it.",
