    {
      "id": "focus-layout-contract",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Layout Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -620,
        "y": 100
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Layout Contract\n\n- focus is the source of semantic baseline\n- representation stays relative to focus\n- layout must not undermine semantic hierarchy\n- panning and zooming alone must not churn authority\n- layout changes should reinforce, not contradict, attention",
